Umar Muhammed, Lafia Governor Abdullahi Sule of Nasarawa State has notified the State House of Assembly of his medical trip to the United States, from Sunday, December 13  2020 to Saturday 29th December 2020. Speaker of the House, Ibrahim Abdullahi, read the governor’s letter to the lawmakers. The letter was titled, ‘Notification to Travel to the United States of America’. The letter read, “I wish to inform the Rt Hon Speaker that I shall be travelling to the United States of America for medical check-up from Sunday, 13th to Saturday 29th Dec. 2020. [READ ALSO] Students abduction: Army making reassuring noises, says Mailafia “Accordingly, in my absence, the deputy Governor would oversee the affairs of the state pending my return.”